title: American horror story freak show -  Meep's funeral/ jimmy meets Esmerelda
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Toulouse is soooo cute and handsome all in one!

It feels funny to hear an English (London accent) in American horror story, I know I sound weird, I’m from London, I remember when I was in America ages I heard some English people talking, sounded like Londoner and I was kind of not happy to hear an English accent, it’s because it feels like I’m back in England, I know it sounds bad for me to say it, lol 😂😈

I'm honestly glad Meep died. I never liked him. I was fine with all the other gruesome stuff the other characters did, but just... I hated the way he mercilessly ripped of animals heads and his boyish nature. I like all the other characters, but Meep, good riddance. But that's my opinion. 😊
